  "text": "There is no doubt that we have to compensate for the CIC filter if we want to use it in the ultrasonic phased array system. In recent years, many researchers have dedicated large efforts to improving frequency magnitude response characteristics by using compensation filters [CITATION_1] [21] [22] [23] [24] . However, most of the compensations are based on decimation CIC filter instead of interpolation CIC filter.",
